*** REPLACE THIS FILE BEFORE PUBLISHING ***

This project is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License,
version 3 (AGPL-3.0). This placeholder exists because the full license
text (~15,000 words) needs to be reproduced byte-for-byte to be legally
correct, and should come from an authoritative source rather than being
reconstructed — do one of the following:

OPTION A (recommended, easiest): When creating the repository on GitHub,
use the built-in "Add a license" step and select "GNU Affero General
Public License v3.0". GitHub inserts the exact, official text
automatically. This will REPLACE this placeholder file.

OPTION B: Download the canonical text directly and overwrite this file:

    curl -o LICENSE https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt

Then verify the file starts with:

    GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE
    Version 3, 19 November 2007

and ends with the "How to Apply These Terms" section.

After replacing this file, add the standard short-form notice near the
top of Cargo.toml files and/or a NOTICE file if you want an additional
human-readable pointer (not required — the LICENSE file alone is
sufficient and is what `license = "AGPL-3.0"` in Cargo.toml refers to).
